Chiltern for Sale for Over $329 Million, Mail on Sunday Reports

-- B y   L i n d s a y   F o r t a d o
-- 
2011-07-31T10:49:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-31/chiltern-for-sale-for-over-329-million-mail-on-sunday-reports.html
Private equity firm Czura Thornton
Ltd. has put Chiltern International Ltd., a clinical research
company, up for sale for more than 200 million pounds ($329
million), the Mail on Sunday reported, without saying where it
got the information.  Czura Thornton has hired  Goldman Sachs Group Inc. (GS)  to
auction Chiltern, and aims to double its investment from when it
bought the company five years ago, the newspaper said. Potential
bidders include CCMP Capital Advisors LLC, the Mail said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lindsay Fortado in London at 
 lfortado@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
